oin our elite team of designers and developers hell bent on improving how people communicate on the Web.</strong></p><p>We&#8217;re looking for someone like us, someone crazy enough to think they can change the Web for the better and skilled and dedicated enough to actually make it happen. If you think you&#8217;re the guy or gal that has the vision, energy and expertise to take SlideDeck to its next, please get in touch.</p><p><strong><a\ntitle=\"product manager\" href=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/careers/dt-labs-product-manager\">LEARN MORE AND APPLY</a></strong></p><p><strong>More about our ideal candidate&#8230;</strong></p><table\nborder=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><td\nstyle=\"text-align: center;\"><img\nclass=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5836\" title=\"Michael Jordan\" src=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/jordan.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br\n/> <em>You get the job done time and time again</em></td><td\nstyle=\"text-align: center;\"><em><img\nclass=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5833\" title=\"Richard Branson\" src=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/branson.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></em><br\n/> <em>You break the rules and set your sights high</em></td></tr><tr><td\nstyle=\"text-align: center;\"><img\nclass=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5834\" title=\"Walt Disney\" src=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/disney.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br\n/> <em>You are creative and dream big</em></td><td\nstyle=\"text-align: center;\"><img\nclass=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5832\" title=\"Borat\" src=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/borat.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br\n/> <em>You&#8217;re not afraid to laugh at your own expense</em></td></tr><tr><td\nstyle=\"text-align: center;\"><img\nclass=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5835\" title=\"Amelia Earhart\" src=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/earhart.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br\n/> <em>Nothing is impossible to you</em><