/div><!--1/3col-->\r\n<div class=\"span8\">\r\n<p>Talent is a scarce resource, and we treasure it. If you\'ve got something for us, we\'d be glad to talk over a cup of coffee. And while you\'re at it, do check out the available opportunities.</p>\r\n</div><!--2/3col-->\r\n</div><!--row-->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"span4\">\r\n<h2>Press Enquiries</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:kangjie.law@openlectures.sg\" class=\"email\"><span class=\"subheader\">kangjie.law</span>@openlectures.sg</a></p>\r\n</div><!--1/3col-->\r\n<div class=\"span8\">\r\n<p>Let us know if you\'re looking to feature <span class=\"openlectures\"><b>open</b>lectures</span> in your publications or media. We\'ve put together some <a href=\"/press\">goodies</a> for you as well, so you can get started straightaway.</p>\r\n</div><!--2/3col-->\r\n</div><!--row-->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"span4\">\r\n<h2>Corporate Affairs</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:corporate@openlectures.sg\" class=\"email\"><span class=\"subheader\">corporate</span>@openlectures.sg</a></p>\r\n</div><!--1/3col-->\r\n<div class=\"span8\">\r\n<p><span class=\"openlectures\"><b>open</b>lectures</span> provides consultancy and videography services for hire. Ask us for a corporate brochure, or if you\'ve got a plan in mind, we\'re all ears.</p>\r\n</div><!--2/3col-->\r\n</div><!--row-->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"span4\">\r\n<h2>Partnerships</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:partnerships@openlectures.sg\" class=\"email\"><span class=\"subheader\">partnerships</span>@openlectures.sg</a></p>\r\n</div><!--1/3col-->\r\n<div class=\"span8\">\r\n<p>Read about <a href=\"/about-us\">our philosophy</a>, and you\'ll realize that we\'re all about giving back. This is for the crazy people who are ready to do crazy things.</p>\r\n</div><!--2/3col-->\r\n</div><!--row-->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"span4\">\r\n<h2>Other Requests</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:contact@openlectures.sg\" class=\"email\"><span class=\"subheade