s/olresponsive/img/facecrop_linan.png\">\r\n			</div><!--pic-->\r\n			<div class=\"spanbio\">\r\n				<p class=\"lead\"><strong>Linan Qiu</strong></p>\r\n				<blockquote>\r\n				<small><cite>Founder and Chief Executive Officer</cite></small>\r\n				<p class=\"bio\">Linan’s job is to make irresistible offers and run the company. He is responsible for the design of the openlectures service, the development of its core infrastructure, and its major day-to-day operations. In his spare time, Linan creates music passionately with his synthesizer. He will attend Columbia College in Fall 2012.</p>\r\n				</blockquote>\r\n			</div><!--bio-->\r\n			<div class=\"spanpic picture\">\r\n				<img src=\"/wp-content/themes/olresponsive/img/facecrop_yitao.png\">\r\n			</div><!--pic-->\r\n			<div class=\"spanbio\">\r\n				<p class=\"lead\"><strong>Zhang Yitao</strong></p>\r\n				<blockquote>\r\n				<small><cite>Founder and Chief Financial Officer</cite></small>\r\n				<p class=\"bio\">Yitao oversees finances and internationalization initiatives, making use of his vast experience in entrepreneurship acquired from his time spent somewhere between Stanford and the Silicon Valley. For leisure, Yitao enjoys sharing his numerous innovative ideas with his partner-in-crime, Linan. He is presently attending Stanford University.</p>\r\n				</blockquote>\r\n			</div><!--bio-->\r\n			<div class=\"spanpic picture\">\r\n				<img src=\"/wp-content/themes/olresponsive/img/facecrop_kenneth.png\">\r\n			</div><!--pic-->\r\n			<div class=\"spanbio\">\r\n				<p class=\"lead\"><strong>Lim Mingjie, Kenneth</strong></p>\r\n				<blockquote><small><cite>Chief Information Officer</cite></small>\r\n				<p class=\"bio\">Kenneth manages the running code riot that powers the openlectures site. He is the brain behind all our \"ghetto\" behind-the-scenes techniques. All crazy concepts are copyright him. He will attend Cornell University in 2013.</p>\r\n				</blockquote>\r\n			</div><!--bio-->\r\n			<div class=\"spanpic picture\">\r\n				<img src=\"/wp-content/themes/olresponsive/img/facecrop_kj.png\">\r\n			</div><!--pic-->\r\n			<div class=\"spanbio\">\r\n				<p class=\"lead\"><strong>Law Kang Jie</strong></p>\r\n				<blockquote><small><cite>Chief Communications Officer</cite></small>\r\n				<p class=\"bio\">Kang Jie talks to everyone. He oversees the outreach, branding and communication strategies implemented. Occasionally, he throws a huge party for our entire team. He will attend the Singapore University of Technology and Design in 2013.</p>\r\n				</blockquote>\r\n			</div><!--bio-->\r\n			<div class=\"spanpic picture\">\r\n				<img src=\"/wp-content/themes/olresponsive/img/facecrop_yj.png\">\r\n			</div><!--pic-->\r\n			<div class=\"spanbio\">\r\n				<p class=\"lead\"><strong>Tek Yong Jian</strong></p>\r\n				<blockquote><small><cite>Chief Operating Officer</cite></small>\r\n				<p class=\"bio\">Yong Jian started as the one-man video editing team. While also takes care of day-to-day operations, he still makes it a point to review every minute of footage to ensure that quality videos are produced. He will attend the National University of Singapore in 2012.</p>\r\n				</blockquote>\r\n			</div><!--bio-->\r\n			<div class=\"spanpic picture\">\r\n				<img src=\"/wp-content/themes/olresponsive/img/facecrop_gary.png\">\r\n			</div><!--pic-->\r\n			<div class=\"spanbio\">\r\n				<p class=\"lead\"><strong>Lee Cheng Feng Gary</strong></p>\r\n				<blockquote><small><cite>Chief Academic Officer</cite></small>\r\n				<p class=\"bio\">Gary manages our formation of lecturers, and is responsible for the direction for content development. He oversees curriculum planning, manpower matters and “anything else”. He will attend Stanford University in 2013.</p>\r\n				</blockquote>\r\n			</div><!--bio-->\r\n		</div><!--row-->\r\n		</div><!--executives-->\r\n		<div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"sponsors\">\r\n			<p class=\"lead\">We are supported by the following organizations and agencies</p>\r\n		